The stationing of PLA troops in Hong Kong is an important symbol of China 's resumed exercise of sovereignty over Hong Kong as well as a special and great mission for the PLA , he said .
At present , preparations in various fields have been under way in a planned and systematic way , he said .
The PLA will bear in mind the important entrustment of the motherland as well as the purpose of the PLA after it stations troops in Hong Kong .
It will also maintain the true political qualities of the army and give its excellent tradition into full play , he said .
He called on PLA soldiers to be stationed in Hong Kong to respect the Hong Kong government , love Hong Kong compatriots and abide by laws of the state and military regulations .
He also called on them to abide by laws in the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region -LRB- HKSAR -RRB- , especially the Basic Law of the HKSAR and Law on Stationing Troop in HKSAR .
They should stand up to tests in whatever complicated situations to contribute to Hong Kong 's long-term prosperity and stability .
`` The officers and rank-and-file of the whole army will steadfastly safeguard the authority of the Party Central Committee with Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core , '' said Liu , noting that `` this is the political wish of Comrade Deng Xiaoping when he was living as well as a requirement of the party , the people and the socialist cause , '' he said .
`` We must carry our work forward at the behest of Comrade Deng Xiaoping , unite more closely around the Party Central Committee and Central Military Commission with Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core to push ahead with the revolutionization , modernization and standardization of the People 's Liberation Army , '' he said .
